  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/ff2eb12678740e4137c9ac24ba906509.avif?t=1761670217\" width=192 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">On Kalia, a once-promising planet, devastation is the indelible mark of a tragic past. A global catastrophe, triggered by a mysterious energy, extinguished an advanced civilization, leaving behind colossal ruins and obscure secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In this desolate setting, Shaktini, a solitary and resilient miner, seeks resources to ensure her survival. Equipped with robotic implants, she ventures through the ruins of Maha Yuga Stambha, a place that holds the key to Kalia's past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Her journey will lead her to unravel the mysteries of the energy that destroyed the ancient civilization and to face the dangers of a hostile world. Shaktini will count on the wisdom of the sage Maharishi, who will guide her in her search for answers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">On Kalia, time is implacable, the challenges are implacable, and the past is revealed in fragments. Shaktini will need to use all her intelligence, strength, and courage to survive and uncover the secrets of the lost civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore the colossal ruins of Maha Yuga Stambha, unraveling their hidden secrets and discovering the history of the lost civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/cd781c8ca380a34fb9df2f0b94d7e36a.poster.avif?t=1761670217\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/cd781c8ca380a34fb9df2f0b94d7e36a.webm?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/cd781c8ca380a34fb9df2f0b94d7e36a.mp4?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Overcome complex obstacles and use your skills to navigate the ruins, jumping, climbing, and dodging dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/22bae99e646c1a7822bd8eb6b143fab1.poster.avif?t=1761670217\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/22bae99e646c1a7822bd8eb6b143fab1.webm?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/22bae99e646c1a7822bd8eb6b143fab1.mp4?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Solve challenging puzzles that will test your intelligence and insight, opening paths to new areas and revealing crucial information about Kalia's past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/15e3f78250d50a91ea946768264bec50.poster.avif?t=1761670217\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/15e3f78250d50a91ea946768264bec50.webm?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/15e3f78250d50a91ea946768264bec50.mp4?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Immerse yourself in a story rich in mysteries, intrigues, and complex characters, with unexpected twists and surprising revelations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Experience the beauty and desolation of Kalia with detailed graphics and an immersive atmosphere.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/ff2eb12678740e4137c9ac24ba906509.avif?t=1761670217\" width=192 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">On Kalia, a once-promising planet, devastation is the indelible mark of a tragic past. A global catastrophe, triggered by a mysterious energy, extinguished an advanced civilization, leaving behind colossal ruins and obscure secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In this desolate setting, Shaktini, a solitary and resilient miner, seeks resources to ensure her survival. Equipped with robotic implants, she ventures through the ruins of Maha Yuga Stambha, a place that holds the key to Kalia's past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Her journey will lead her to unravel the mysteries of the energy that destroyed the ancient civilization and to face the dangers of a hostile world. Shaktini will count on the wisdom of the sage Maharishi, who will guide her in her search for answers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">On Kalia, time is implacable, the challenges are implacable, and the past is revealed in fragments. Shaktini will need to use all her intelligence, strength, and courage to survive and uncover the secrets of the lost civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore the colossal ruins of Maha Yuga Stambha, unraveling their hidden secrets and discovering the history of the lost civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/cd781c8ca380a34fb9df2f0b94d7e36a.poster.avif?t=1761670217\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/cd781c8ca380a34fb9df2f0b94d7e36a.webm?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/cd781c8ca380a34fb9df2f0b94d7e36a.mp4?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Overcome complex obstacles and use your skills to navigate the ruins, jumping, climbing, and dodging dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/22bae99e646c1a7822bd8eb6b143fab1.poster.avif?t=1761670217\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/22bae99e646c1a7822bd8eb6b143fab1.webm?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/22bae99e646c1a7822bd8eb6b143fab1.mp4?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Solve challenging puzzles that will test your intelligence and insight, opening paths to new areas and revealing crucial information about Kalia's past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/15e3f78250d50a91ea946768264bec50.poster.avif?t=1761670217\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/15e3f78250d50a91ea946768264bec50.webm?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038010/extras/15e3f78250d50a91ea946768264bec50.mp4?t=1761670217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Immerse yourself in a story rich in mysteries, intrigues, and complex characters, with unexpected twists and surprising revelations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Experience the beauty and desolation of Kalia with detailed graphics and an immersive atmosphere.</p>",
